'''华人长老会教堂'''或雪梨華人長老會（Chinese Presbyterian Church，CPC）是一个[[长老会|长老会]]堂会，也是[[澳洲|澳洲]]现存最古老的华人教会<ref>{{cite book|last=Mar|first=W.L.|title=So Great A Cloud Of Witness: A history of the Chinese Presbyterian Church Sydney 1893–1993|year=1993|publisher=Chinese Presbyterian Church|isbn=0646138340|page=1}}</ref>。2017年，该堂约有600人，礼拜语言使用[[英语|英语]]、[[粤语|粤语]]和[[普通话|普通话]]。

该堂创建于1893年，1957年迁入Crown街和Albion街转角的富勒顿纪念教堂现址<ref>{{cite book|last=Jupp|first=James|author-link=James Jupp|title=The Australian People: An Encyclopedia of the Nation, Its People and Their Origins|year=2001|publisher=Cambridge University Press|page=210|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=yTKFBXfCI1QC&pg=PA210|access-date=2015-02-06|archive-date=2015-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206030533/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=yTKFBXfCI1QC&pg=PA210|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

